<tr><th class="brewing">Cooking & Baking From The Heart</th><th class="brewing">Brewing & Making Drinks from the Heart</th></tr>
<tr><th class="cooking">I believe in the famous saying of Mary Berry, 'Cooking and baking is both physical and mental therapy. It brings happiness and calm to me. When it comes to cooking and baking cupcakes, I always choose the best ingredients to cook and to bake not only beautiful cupcakes, but also delicious Filipino dish. Baking cookies, breads, desserts, and other sweet products are my favorite part of being one of the baker, at the same time a chef,in this cafe because every time I bake or cook I always put love on them.</th>
<th class="cooking"> Experimenting drinks is the most fun to do. You can discover new taste of something. Being a barista in the day and bar tender in the night was not so challenging for me. Starting from grinding different coffee beans to using filter, percolator and French press. Then, pouring hot water onto the ground coffee beans, water seeps through the ground coffee, absorbing its constituent chemical compounds, and then passes through a filter resulted to freshly coffee serve just for you. To mixing different alcohol and non alcohol drink,  I always give my best to serve all my customers. </tr>
